---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="PawDore privacy policy - how we handle your data."
>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="post-content">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p><em>Last updated: March 31, 2026</em></p>

      <p>
        PawDore ("we", "us", or "our") operates pawdore.com. This page informs you of our policies
        regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information when you visit our website.
      </p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

      <p>
        PawDore is a static website and we collect minimal data. We do not require user accounts
        or collect personal information directly. However, third-party services we use may collect
        some data as described below.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies and Tracking</h2>

      <p>
        Our affiliate partners (including Amazon) may use cookies to track referrals. These cookies
        are governed by the respective privacy policies of those partners. We may also use analytics
        tools to understand how visitors use our site, which may collect anonymized usage data.
      </p>

      <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>

      <p>
        Our site contains affiliate links to products on third-party websites. When you click these
        links, you will be redirected to external sites with their own privacy policies. We encourage
        you to review those policies before making a purchase.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>

      <p>
        If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at <strong>hello@pawdore.com</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
